<s> Editor's Note DESIGNING WEB PAGES FOR SIGHT IMPAIRED USERS  </s>
<s> If you are involved in making Web pages accessible for users with sight impairments, check out "Disabled Accessibility: The Pragmatic  </s>
<s> Approach," by Jakob Nielsen ("The Alertbox," June 13, 1999 issue).  </s>
<s> Nielsen includes a link to the W3 Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 1.0, the W3's prioritized list of design rules, and a very useful checklist for Web page designers.  </s>
